#~ "contributed to all areas of the game, from mainline content shipped as "
#~ "part of the official releases to hundreds of player-made projects "
#~ "available to download from our add-ons server. Whether you need help "
#~ "beating a particular scenario or adding a feature to your custom maps, "
#~ "<cite>Wesnoth</cite> boasts a massive community of players and creators "
#~ "always willing to help."
#~ msgstr ""
